                            Project - Underground Pipework
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 grid-item project hotel" data-category="hotel">
                <div class="portfolio-item">
                    <div class="pt-img"><a href="~/src/gallery/P-02.jpg" class="image" title="Project - Laundry Installation"><img src="~/src/gallery/P-02_2.jpg" alt=""></a></div>
